{"id": "1180852700573859970", "channel_id": "1180852700573859970", "type": 0, "author_id": "368770460617408515", "author_name": "0314_0", "author_bot": false, "content": "請問關於今天修復的BUG「未經確認多次抽取」不是用已經有的數量去抽取嗎? 怎麼看有人的留言的意思好像變成是能額外一直抽? 因為內文表達的意思並不像是按太快速能在沒有抽數的情況下無限抽，還是真的有人是在沒抽數的情況下一直抽? 想問這是誤解錯誤謠傳還是實際狀況確實如此", "timestamp": "2023-12-03T12:47:02.999000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1180852700829724722", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 585721, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1180852700573859970/1180852700829724722/image.png?ex=69cc6b07&is=69cb1987&hm=34620827b0eb91f0ab8643811fac33e93c553026fb02ceb7aaf013192b87c606&"}, {"id": "1180852701072998420", "filename": "1701607514237.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 63841, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1180852700573859970/1180852701072998420/1701607514237.jpg?ex=69cc6b07&is=69cb1987&hm=f669508fbd6917923dba9bc1f54744728d72109a917a078f423238ad9ec15a84&"}, {"id": "1180852701286891590", "filename": "1701607526979.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 31090, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1180852700573859970/1180852701286891590/1701607526979.jpg?ex=69cc6b07&is=69cb1987&hm=a4ba9177639529a9edf713e941dbecc875ff848c691ca49eefbff4d448eb2c97&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1180852700573859970", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」連續點選「喚醒抽取」的按鈕太頻繁時可能導致未經確認多次抽取的問題。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1186103872205369424"]}
